{"arkId":"cl010100761","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010100761","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1685 - 1700 (bo\u00eetier et cadran) et 1700 - 1715 (mouvement)","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1685,"endYear":1700,"imprecision":"","text":"Fin du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""},{"startYear":1700,"endYear":1715,"imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Enderlin, Andr\u00e9","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 10079","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ronde ; fond d\u00e9cor\u00e9 d\u0027un bouquet de fleurs de couleurs chaudes nou\u00e9 d\u0027un ruban bleu. Sur la carrure, entre deux liser\u00e9s se trouve un treillage reprennant les tons jaune, orang\u00e9 et bleu du fond. Contre-\u00e9mail bleu turquoise orn\u00e9 d\u0027une banderole avec devise : Temps perdu\/n\u0027est a Recouvrer\/sage est quil le s\u00e7ait\/employer. Sur la lunette du verre, frise de fleurettes et de triangle de m\u00eames couleurs que le fond et le cadran. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains en \u00e9mail noir, centre d\u00e9cor\u00e9 d\u0027une peinture de fleurs similaire \u00e0 celle du fond. Aiguille reperc\u00e9e et grav\u00e9e. Echappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre, balancier \u00e0 ressort-spiral-r\u00e9glant couvert d\u0027un coq en argent reperc\u00e9 et grav\u00e9 de rinceaux. Piliers en argent, rosette en argent num\u00e9rot\u00e9e de I \u00e0 XII.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9: ENDERLIN A BALE ; bo\u00eetier sign\u00e9 : Braun f.","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"5,4","displayDimension":"5,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"4","displayDimension":"4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,1","displayDimension":"2,1 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)","placeOfCreation":"B\u00e2le (Europe-\u003ESuisse)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Claudius C\u00f4te (1881-1956), Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"16\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"09\/07\/1961","startYear